track_notes: A linear walk from Honister Slate Mine over Fleetwith Pike (LDW-116) Haystacks (LDW-131) High Crag (LDW-065) High Stile itself and Red Pike (LDW-062). The Honister Rambler 77/77A Bus will take you back to the slate mine.
track_title: High Stile linear walk with 4 Wainwrights

track_notes: From the carpark follow the forest road for about 4km. Just past the YHA and Field Study centre there is a gate turn left up a firebreak and follow the path to the summit ridge. Normally you would visit Red Pike on the way to High Stile but when I did this track the mist was so thick I didnt bother. Allow about 2.5 hours.
